track_notes: Just parc the car at the sky resort and choose the summit you want. It is convenient to leave stuff at the car as you can park in between the two summits; very nice panorama from the Bernarde to Cervin and Mont Viso

I put this track because it has been done in winter with snow. First the road is closed! I trepass and went nearly a the end of the road, just because i have a 4 whell drive and knew the place. the walk is not so easy and sleepy; if you are fit enought you can go to the summit Picogu F/AM-369
Easy when there is no snow; the sloope could be sleepy with ice. Nice panorama, plenty room to park and to setup antenna.
Starting from Touyet villege, you can parm along the road, get some water in summertime, and snowshoes may be needed in wintertime.
track_title: The long way to summit from Touyet
